Mrs Mudavadi, 92, was the widow of the former powerful Cabinet Minister Moses Mudavadi.President Kenyatta described the late Mrs Mudavadi as a devoted, generous and humble matriarch. President Uhuru Kenyatta on Monday sent his message of condolences to the Mudavadi family following the death of Mrs Hannah Atsianzale Mudavadi.
Mrs Mudavadi, 92, the widow of the former powerful Cabinet Minister Moses Mudavadi and the mother of ANC party leader Musalia Mudavadi, died early on Monday morning at Nairobi Hospital where she had been admitted.



